    "lines": [
      {
        "type": "narration",
        "character": null,
        "text": "在王座散发出的神圣余晖中，空气仿佛凝固了一般。所有人都还沉浸在刚才战胜BOSS和发现‘诸王的王座’带来的狂热情绪里。但随着时间流逝，兴奋感逐渐褪去，取而代之的是对新权力结构、公会运作模式的理性审视。"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "铃木悟 (Suzuki Satoru)",
        "text": "*扫视四周，动作平稳* 大家的情绪都比较高涨。",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "emotion_intensity": 3,
        "outfit": "casual"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "铃木悟 (Suzuki Satoru)",
        "text": "不过，这种状态可不太持续的吧？",
        "emotion": "worried",
        "emotion_intensity": 4,
        "outfit": "casual"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "铃木悟 (Suzuki Satoru)",
        "text": "*微微侧身* 我们需要把注意力重新聚焦到流程上。",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "emotion_intensity": 5,
        "outfit": "casual"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "塔其米 (Tachimi)",
        "text": "悟说得对。",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "emotion_intensity": 5,
        "outfit": "dark_robe"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "塔其米 (Tachimi)",
        "text": "*环视四周，目光扫过众人* 过度的兴奋只会让人忽略关键信息。",
        "emotion": "worried",
        "emotion_intensity": 4,
        "outfit": "dark_robe"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "塔其米 (Tachimi)",
        "text": "我们得冷静下来，分析一下接下来的每一步。",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "emotion_intensity": 3,
        "outfit": "dark_robe"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "乌尔贝特·阿兰·奥德 (Ulbert Alain Ode)",
        "text": "*嗤笑一声* 分析？",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "emotion_intensity": 3,
        "outfit": "black_trenchcoat"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "乌尔贝特·阿兰·奥德 (Ulbert Alain Ode)",
        "text": "你们的理性可真是让人乏味。",
        "emotion": "angry",
        "emotion_intensity": 4,
        "outfit": "black_trenchcoat"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "乌尔贝特·阿兰·奥德 (Ulbert Alain Ode)",
        "text": "难道战胜了神祇，就该像个会计师一样斤斤计较吗？",
        "emotion": "scornful",
        "emotion_intensity": 5,
        "outfit": "black_trenchcoat"
      },
      {
        "type": "narration",
        "character": null,
        "text": "**分析目标：** 描绘从战胜BOSS的兴奋期，过渡到塔其米要求冷静分析，乌尔贝特用轻蔑态度进行挑衅的瞬间。氛围需要从“亢奋”转向“紧张/对抗”。 **关键元素提炼：** 1.  **地点环境：** 王座散发的神圣余晖（背景光源）。 2.  **情绪变化：** 兴奋 $\\rightarrow$ 冷静审视 $\\rightarrow$ 冲突。 3.  **核心动作/状态：** 群体停顿、空气凝固感增强。"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "布钮萌",
        "text": "哼，乌尔贝特。",
        "emotion": "angry",
        "emotion_intensity": 5,
        "outfit": "dark_robe"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "布钮萌",
        "text": "*上前一步，语气强硬* 别用这种态度。",
        "emotion": "serious",
        "emotion_intensity": 4,
        "outfit": "dark_robe"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "布钮萌",
        "text": "战胜BOSS只是开始，我们必须规划接下来的每一步。",
        "emotion": "worried",
        "emotion_intensity": 3,
        "outfit": "dark_robe"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "未知",
        "text": "*轻笑一声* 两位都有些激动了。",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "emotion_intensity": 3,
        "outfit": "trench_coat"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "character": "未知",
        "text": "*扫视全场，目光平静* 情绪的波动只会消耗精力。",
        "emotion": "worried",
        "emotion_intensity": 4,
        "outfit": "trench_coat"
      },
      {
        "type": "dialogue",
